OL,3,CThe urgent crisis in children's reading
OL,5,FBut, today, these books are struggling
OL,6,Fto capture children's imaginations in
OL,7,Fthe same way.
OL,9,FReading for pleasure amongst under 18s
OL,10,Fhas hit a 'crisis' point with the
OL,11,Fnumber enjoying it in their free time
OL,12,Fdropping to just one in three.
OL,14,FSo, what's behind this? And what are
OL,15,Fthe long-term impacts?
